  "text": "One person performed all the detailed video coding for the phone-related sequences using an updated version of FOTware [CITATION_1] , a tool for the analysis of naturalistic driving data. Each sequence was coded according to these variables: Eyes on road, Turning, Road type, Lead vehicle present, Oncoming vehicle present, and Weather conditions. These variables, further described below, contain mutually exclusive categories. The sequences were coded as time series with 10 Hz resolution. A total of about 1 h and 30 min of driving was coded.",
